{{Module}}

== Overview ==
This nifty module boosts the amount of credits won in outland events and battles by 20%. The effect is cumulative.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Bounty Enhancer can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
